siteMetadata.title: Southeast Data Librarian Symposium 2019
siteMetadata.description: Website for the 2019 Southeast Data Librarian Symposium (SEDLS). The SEDLS is intended to provide a low-cost opportunity for librarians and other research data specialists to gather and explore developments in the field of data librarianship, including the management and sharing of research data.
